      <h1 class='title'>Freedom of Information Act</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 28 November 2002 vol 395 c58WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_58ws' title='Col. 58WS &mdash; HC Deb 28 November 2002 vol 395 c58WS' name='column_58ws' href='#column_58ws' rel='bookmark'>58WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0395P2_20021128_CWS_21'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-yvette-cooper' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0395P2_20021128_CWS_21' title='Link to this speech by Ms Yvette Cooper' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-yvette-cooper" title="Ms Yvette Cooper">The Parliamentary Secretary, Lord Chancellor's Department (Yvette Cooper)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">My right honourable and noble Friend the Lord Chancellor has today announced that, in accordance with section 87 (5) of the <a href="/acts/freedom-of-information-act-2000">Freedom of Information Act 2000</a>, he has laid before Parliament the annual report on the progress made in implementing the <a href="/acts/freedom-of-information-act-2000">Freedom of Information Act 2000</a>. Copies of the Report will be placed in the Libraries of both Houses. A copy of the Report on the review of legislation prohibiting the disclosure of information will also be placed in the Libraries of both Houses.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
